;; ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
;; descriptor-shape-sweep — 2026-07-14
;; Lane: descriptor-shape sweep (SRE honesty pass)
;; Author: Descriptor-Shape Sweep lane (Lacuna Eng)
;; Date: 2026-07-14
;;
;; Alfred's floor doctrine — "We can't lie to people. They trust us."
;;
;; A verb registered as "wired" that returns a tagged-list descriptor
;; like (part/bow) or (motion/move-to target 10 20) — WITHOUT doing the
;; thing — is a lie. Same category as stubs, just harder to spot.
;;
;; Method:
;;   1. Boot the full env (all installers + reference registrar).
;;   2. Call every bound verb with 0..5 sentinel args.
;;   3. Detect return shape: [name, ...args] or [Sym(name), ...args]
;;      where the head equals the verb name.
;;   4. Cross-check reference :signature and :examples.
;;   5. Categorize:
;;      - REAL-IMPL         — substrate exists; wire it.
;;      - SUBSTRATE-DEFERRED — needs infra not on disk; mark deferred.
;;      - RE-SPEC           — signature unclear; needs Alfred review.
;;
;; Total descriptor-shape verbs: 779
;; Split: REAL-IMPL=89 | SUBSTRATE-DEFERRED=685 | RE-SPEC=5
;;
;; Note on scanner: the scanner boots the ENTIRE production env stack
;; (base + AI + game + game-theory + game-instances + prefab + sprite +
;; juggle + scene + cine + ops + commercial + auth + system + topo +
;; wired-verbs + priya + hana + marcus + ada + reference-registrar).
;; Everything a real user's REPL sees is inspected. Verbs picked up here
;; are the ones a kid at the REPL would find lying about their behavior.
;;
;; ─── Top 15 substrates by unblocked-verb count ────────────────────────
;;   world-runtime           = 46   (kira-world)
;;   ops-runtime             = 45   (zain-ops)
;;   calc-numerical          = 43   (hana-calc-more)   REAL-IMPL bucket
;;   entity-effect-runtime   = 43   (ren-motion)
;;   topo-algebra            = 41   (rin-topo)         REAL-IMPL bucket
;;   sound-composition       = 38   (yuki-note)
;;   card-runtime            = 37   (toshi-card)      *high priority
;;   framebuffer-state-layer = 35   (hana-paint)      *high priority
;;   grid-CA-host            = 34   (ada-grid)        *high priority
;;   radio-runtime           = 32   (yuki-radio)
;;   conway-world            = 31   (ada-conway)     *high priority
;;   nav-map-runtime         = 29   (sora-misc)
;;   ai-behavior-runtime     = 28   (kenji-ai)
;;   choreography-engine     = 25   (ren-motion)      *high priority
;;   camera-state            = 24   (emiko-camera)
;;
;; ─── Alfred's priority substrates (from mandate) ──────────────────────
;;   card-runtime            → 37 verbs unblocked
;;   conway-world            → 31 verbs unblocked
;;   grid-CA-host            → 34 verbs unblocked
;;   framebuffer-state-layer → 35 verbs unblocked
;;   form-registry           → 6 verbs unblocked (small but load-bearing)
;;   choreography-engine     → 25 verbs unblocked
;;   TOTAL priority-first    = 168 verbs / 779 (21.6%)
;;
;; If Alfred builds ALL SIX priority substrates: 168 lies → 168 truths.
;;
;; ─── Recommended lane assignments (existing lanes) ────────────────────
;;   kira lane        → world-runtime (46) + game-runtime-extras (15) +
;;                      collision (2) + prefab (2) + group (5) + object (4)
;;                      = 74 verbs
;;   ren-motion lane  → entity-effect-runtime (43) + choreography-engine
;;                      (25) = 68 verbs
;;   hana lane        → calc-numerical (43) + framebuffer-state-layer (35)
;;                      + surface (17) + plot (7) + text (2) = 104 verbs
;;   yuki lane        → sound-composition (38) + radio (32) + audio-hw
;;                      (12) + time-scheduler (13) + pattern (2) +
;;                      podcast-adapter (via priya) = ~97 verbs
;;   ada lane         → card-runtime (37) + grid-CA-host (34) +
;;                      conway-world (31) + form-registry (6) +
;;                      app-registry (6) + core-dispatch (13) +
;;                      emoji (4) + ctx / floor / wait / base
;;                      = ~131 verbs
;;   kenji lane       → ai-behavior (28) + ai-inference (8) +
;;                      ai-planning (4) = 40 verbs
;;   sora lane        → nav-map (29) + weather (2) + flower (4) +
;;                      artifact (6) + route-domain (4) + sprite (3)
;;                      = 48 verbs
;;   zain lane        → ops-runtime (45) = 45 verbs
;;   nao lane         → commercial-adapter (21) + shoppe (7) = 28 verbs
;;   emiko lane       → camera-state (24) + scene (8) + juggle (6) = 38
;;   rin lane         → topo-algebra (41) = 41 verbs
;;   toshi lane       → part-pose (18) + particle-system (17) = 35 verbs
;;   marcus lane      → symbolic-cas (via sym/) if elevated to REAL-IMPL
;;   jess lane        → alg-remainder (via alg/) + chem/balance
;;   hiroshi lane     → input-runtime (5) + system-runtime-extras (9)
;;   priya lane       → podcast-adapter (already-partial)
;;
;;   TOTAL if every lane covers its assignment: 779 verbs de-lied.
;; ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

